First Department,

February, 1977

(February 3, 1977) Benjamin Andrews, Respondent, v Kenneth E. Williams, Defendant, and State Insurance Fund, Appellant.

Order, Supreme Court, New York County, entered on March 31, 1976, unanimously affirmed on the opinion of Nadel, J., at Trial Term, without costs and without disbursements. Concur—Lupiano, J. P., Birns, Lane and Markewich, JJ. [89 Misc 2d 492.]
